#

Seared Pork Tenderloin with Apple Cider Gravy and Garlic Smashed Potatoes

$18.5
650 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Tags:

PorkComfort FoodFall Flavors

Description

A succulent pork tenderloin seared to perfection, paired with a tangy apple cider gravy, and creamy garlic smashed potatoes for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • Apple Cider: 1 cup
  • Chicken Broth: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic Cloves: 4, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Red Potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tsp, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
